{"tid":2329190,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"一名八十歲屬歌舞群組的支那肺炎患者不治","createTime":"2020-12-17T05:15:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-17T06:49:14.000Z","uid":25240,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"f3582ce6258e55bb161be4d13b9c7a22862f288a","tid":2329190,"uid":25240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T05:15:12.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】消息指，本港新增逾90宗新冠病毒確診個案，歌舞群組一名80歲患者不治，疫情至今124人死亡。<br />\n<br />\n80歲老翁到過旺角金雞廣場金儷星，最初沒有病徵，上月23日因發燒在大埔那打素醫院治療，之後情況惡化，本月3日轉送深切治療部，最終不治。<br />\n<br />\n歌舞群組是疫情以來最大的感染群組，累計722人確診。"},{"pid":"ec7cf6496af81ccd86355a322799258d61ad86e7","tid":2329190,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T06:49:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/gun.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/gun.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/gun.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}